name: Schiffrin & Longo P.C. Law Office
overview: Schiffrin & Longo P.C. Law Office provides lawyers for trademarks and intellectual property. We understand that a company’s name and brand are its most important foundation and therefore need to be protected. Since this is our entire practice, you know we can provide the most information to you and adequately protect your rights. We provide legal and reasonably priced services for trademarks, copyrights, Internet issues, false advertising and unfair competition.
